\taxon{Definition}
\title{Tangent Bundle}
\p{
The tangent bundle of #{ {\cal M} } is the disjoint union of all [tangent spaces](0075):
##{ {\rm T}{\cal M}\ =\ \{(\mathbf{x},\mathbf{v})\ \mid\ \mathbf{x}\in{\cal M},\ {\rm and}\ \mathbf{v}\in{\rm T}_{\mathbf{x}}{\cal M}\} }
}
